audio_descriptions.notes:
In the dark to one side of the stage are domes of glowing bars, each one with a child dressed in white inside. Emme, J Lo's daughter, sings in one.

Emme joins her mother on stage. J-Lo is wearing a long red, white, and blue feathered coat. When she holds it wide, it is the flag of Puerto Rico.
